                  Safety First
                </h3>
                <p class="font-body text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  We reduce risks with drone technology that keeps people and
                  property safe.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- Eco-Responsibility Card -->
              <div
                class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-accent/20 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
              >
                <div
                  class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full mb-6"
                >
